{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-templates-post-template-js","path":"/android-img-update-uri/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"slug":"/android-img-update-uri/","date":"2020.01.12","tags":["Android"],"title":"AndroidのImageViewを同じUriで更新する","description":"AndroidのImageViewを同じUriで更新する方法を調べたので備忘録。","thumbnail":{"name":"android-thumbnail","publicURL":"/static/android-thumbnail-831e89b5542535363c21ffdc58e26dc5.png"}},"html":"<h2 id=\"ハマったところ\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E3%83%8F%E3%83%9E%E3%81%A3%E3%81%9F%E3%81%A8%E3%81%93%E3%82%8D\" aria-label=\"ハマったところ permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ハマったところ</h2>\n<p>ImageViewの画像をUriで指定したいとき下記のようにやると思います。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-kotlin line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-kotlin\"><span class=\"token keyword\">val</span> imageView <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> findViewById<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ImageView<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>R<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>imageView<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nimageView<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setImageURI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>uri<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>ですが、setImageURIは、その時点でImageViewに設定されているuriと同じuriを引数に渡した場合、たとえ画像ファイルの中身が変更されていてもViewを更新してくれません。</p>\n<h2 id=\"解決方法\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\" aria-label=\"解決方法 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>解決方法</h2>\n<p>一度引数にnullで設定した後に、もう一度uriをを指定する。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"kotlin\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-kotlin line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-kotlin\"><span class=\"token keyword\">val</span> imageView <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> findViewById<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>ImageView<span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>R<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>imageView<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nimageView<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setImageURI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nimageView<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setImageURI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>uri<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/android-img-update-uri/#%E3%83%8F%E3%83%9E%E3%81%A3%E3%81%9F%E3%81%A8%E3%81%93%E3%82%8D\">ハマったところ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/android-img-update-uri/#%E8%A7%A3%E6%B1%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\">解決方法</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/android-img-update-uri/"}}}